 2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
 4. the dutch is not the fan of dubstep##6
 5. the fan of d&b is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the dutch is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 9. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
13. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
14. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
15. the indian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5

.:: Answer ::.
