.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, indie, trance
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, sports, spy, fantasy
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 9. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the fan of indie is not the person watching zombie movies##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola      | sprite  | soy-milk | juice        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | house   | indie    | dubstep      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | fantasy | spy   | zombie    |

